      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Oct 2010 16:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[Do you want to <b>lose inches off your waistline</b> in the first 2 weeks without starving, without depriving, and without doing anything harmful or unnatural? Well, take just a little bit of time out of your hectic day to day to read this article here and discover 3 important tips that helped me lose inches and melt fat off lightning fast!<br />
<br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_iBaogoSxAIo/TI-nY4BIjyI/AAAAAAAACS8/l1PnpB6MT74/s1600/slim+down+waist.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_iBaogoSxAIo/TI-nY4BIjyI/AAAAAAAACS8/l1PnpB6MT74/s320/slim+down+waist.jpg" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br />
</div><br />
1.) Alright, the first thing you are going to want to do is make sure that you are getting 100% proper nutrition WITHOUT restricting nutrients. You must make sure that you are getting protein, complex carbs such as fiber and whole grains, healthy fats such as omega and monounsaturated, and foods rich in vitamins and minerals (fruits/vegetables.)<br />
<br />
I highly recommend that you don't get caught up with those popular fad diets you see everywhere you turn. Those types of programs are based around restricting particular types of nutrients and/or calories from your diet... and that's a big no-no! Restricting calories and/or important nutrients will ultimately cause your metabolism to decrease... which leads to yo-yo weight loss and your body will store fat on you instead of burning it off!<br />
<br />
2.) The next thing you are going to want to do is make sure that you increase your metabolism to the maximum peak... NATURALLY! Do not boost your metabolic rate with unnatural methods such as diet pills or some other type of dangerous fad. What you want to do to get the best results is to boost your metabolism with using nothing but proper nutrition.<br />
<br />
Doing that will yield the best results, and not to mention, since you are increasing your metabolism naturally, once you lose the weight... it stays off!<br />
<br />
3.) Okay, now the final thing that you want to do in order to <b>lose inches off your waistline</b> lightning fast is to eat multiple times daily (4-5 small healthy meals) instead of the usual 2-3 large meals. The reason being is twofold. Firstly, you will not starve due to the frequent small meals you'll be eating during the day. Secondly, by eating more frequently through out the day, you will end up causing your metabolism to SKYROCKET to the maximum peak... consistently.<br />
<br />
