      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Oct 2010 16:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[Do you want to <b>lose 15 lbs. fast</b>, easy, and keep it off permanently? Read on to discover the top 5 weight loss tips to get slim lightning fast and with ease!<br />
<br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_iBaogoSxAIo/TI-mrH7iJZI/AAAAAAAACS0/Jbl7u0yTdq8/s1600/fastweightloss.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_iBaogoSxAIo/TI-mrH7iJZI/AAAAAAAACS0/Jbl7u0yTdq8/s320/fastweightloss.jpg" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br />
</div><br />
#1.) Increase the amount of water you drink to 1/2 your body weight in ounces. So, if you weigh 150 pounds, you would drink 75 ounces of water each day. What is drinking this much water going to do? Well, let's see here:<br />
<br />
* You are going to get rid of harmful toxins in your body that are keeping fat cells on you!<br />
* You will be assisting your body in quickly building and repairing muscle tissue. The more muscle tissue you have on your body... the more you will automatically burn away stubborn fat!<br />
* Drinking a lot of water will cause your body to release water from your body (better known as water weight).<br />
<br />
Just watch what happens after drinking plenty of water for the first week! You are going to notice a tremendous difference in how you look and feel!<br />
<br />
#2.) Get ALL nutrients in your diet! Do not fall for those low carb, low fat, low calorie types of programs. Restricting nutrients from your body is only going to cause your metabolism to decrease. And if your metabolism decreases... this ultimately leads to STORED body fat and yo-yo weight loss!<br />
<br />
#3.) Sleep 7-8 hours every night and keep your body at room temperature. Getting plenty of sleep EVERY NIGHT will allow your body to burn calories and build muscle tissue while you rest! You can actually burn up to 500 calories or more just by getting a full nights rest!<br />
<br />
#4.) Make sure that you increase your metabolism and prevent it from decreasing. The faster you get your metabolic rate with NATURAL METHODS, the faster you are going to lose pounds of fat. Not only that, since boosting your metabolism is a natural weight loss methods, once you lose the weight... it will stay off for good.<br />
<br />
Now please take my advice on this... AVOID diet pills and fad diets for many reasons, but also because those things will SLOW your metabolism down! Did you know that the consequence of a slow metabolism is that your body will begin to STORE fat instead of burning it off, and also your body will end up with yo-yo weight loss (you lose weight and then the weight comes right back on)!<br />
<br />
#5.) The final tip to help you <b>lose 15 lbs. fast</b> is the most important... STAY CONSISTENT! Consistency is the absolute most important part of dieting.<br />
<br />
