      <content:encoded><![CDATA[To <b>lose 25 lbs. in 4 weeks</b>, it DOES NOT take a miracle and it IS easy to do... contrary to what you always hear, see, and read! In this article here, I'll explain the top 4 ways to make losing a lot of weight in a short period of time possible!<br />
