<br />
The reason why this is so important is due the fact that if you start when you are not ready, you will find it more harder to stick with your program.<br />
<br />
Make sure you make a plan for your weight loss goals and do what you can to get yourself motivated to start. It could be setting a special date to begin, etc.<br />
<br />
2.) Nutrition, FIRST! - Never put diet pills, exercise, or anything else above making sure that you are getting 100% proper nutrition in your plan. NOTHING will ever work unless you are eating properly.<br />
