      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Sep 2010 16:27:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[In order to <b>lose 25 pounds every month</b>, there are a couple of things that you can do and there a couple things you should avoid. In this article, we are going to cover what those things are so that you can FINALLY get that body you deserve!<br />
