      <content:encoded><![CDATA[Are you ready to finally <b>get rid of excess fat</b> fast, easy, and permanently? Okay, take just a couple of minutes out of your day to read this article here and learn more about 5 proven ways to get extreme fat loss starting today!<br />
<br />
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_iBaogoSxAIo/TI-iK5poOVI/AAAAAAAACSU/5oqVnOYc_FU/s1600/best+fat+loss+system.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_iBaogoSxAIo/TI-iK5poOVI/AAAAAAAACSU/5oqVnOYc_FU/s320/best+fat+loss+system.jpg" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br />
</div><br />
1.) Increase Your Metabolism - The faster you get your metabolic rate, the faster you are going to melt away pounds of fat. On the flip side, the slower your metabolism is, the slower you are going to lose weight.<br />
<br />
To prevent your metabolism from decreasing, make sure you DO NOT fad diet (low carb, low fat, low calorie, etc.). Also, I highly recommend that you avoid diet pills. Yes, they do mention that they will boost your metabolism, but what do you think is going to happen when you stop taking them?<br />
<br />
To increase your metabolism naturally, I highly recommend you do so with proper nutrition. There are a couple of well know diets that will boost your metabolism with proper nutrition.<br />
<br />
2.) Speaking Of Nutrition - Be sure that you get ALL types of nutrients in your diet for best results. Your body LOVES many different types of nutrients and when you restrict getting any of them, you are going to make your body upset... hence your metabolism slowing down as mentioned in #1!<br />
<br />
I recommend that you get protein, fiber, healthy fats (such as monounsaturated, polyunsaturated, and Omega), and foods rich in vitamins and minerals such as fruits (especially apples and berries), and vegetables (especially greener veggies such as broccoli and spinach).<br />
<br />
3.) Plan - Never begin dieting without planning. "Failing to plan is planning to fail".<br />
<br />
4.) K.I.S.S (keep it simple stupid) - Do not make dieting so complicated if you want to truly get lightning fast results. Why is that? Well, the more easier you approach losing weight, the easier it will be to stick with your plan. There are many easy diet programs out there and those are the types I recommend you go on... especially if you have a hard time sticking with a diet.<br />
<br />
5.) Consistency Is Key - One of the most popular quotes in N.F.L football is simple... FINISH! You want to <a href="http://www.fatlossin11days.info/"><b>get rid of excess fat fast</b></a>... you have to FINISH whatever it is you do to reach that goal. Fat is stubborn, and it will not be removed if you are not 100% consistent with what it is you are doing to reach your goals.<br />
<br />
You can do it! Trust in yourself, plan before you start, keep it simple, and FINISH!<br />
<br />
