      <pubDate>Wed, 26 May 2010 12:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[The first thing you need to do if you want to <b><a href="http://www.everyotherdaydiet.com/go/ajbarnes" rel="nofollow">get a thin waist fas</a></b>t is to make sure that with whatever it is you do, STAY CONSISTENT! The next thing I recommend for you to do is to follow my top 5 tips for losing inches off your waistline fast and easy!
<br />
<br />1.) Proper Nutrition - Eat 4-5 small healthy meals each day. Make sure that each of these meals contain ALL nutrients (protein, complex carbs such as fiber, healthy fats, vitamins, and minerals). Restricting nutrients and/or calories will only slow down your metabolism... so stay away from "fad dieting" also!
<br />
<br />2.) Exercise - Be sure to do both aerobic and resistance training to yield the best results. One tip I would like to add to this one is to lose inches quicker off your waist, I highly recommend for you to do leg raises for direct exercising on the waist and the incline treadmill for indirect exercising.
<br />
<br />3.) Water - Drink 1/2 your body weight in ounces every day. Water is absolutely essential for properly metabolizing fat and of course for many other health concerns.
<br />
<br />4.) Sleep - Aim to get 7-8 hours of rest each and every night. Doing so will ensure that your body will be able to properly get rid of fat waste while you sleep. Did you know that your body can burn up to 500 calories while you sleep?! That's right! So, make sure you start getting more sleep!
<br />
<br />5.) Metabolic Rate - The way to guarantee that you'll get a thin waist fast is to make sure that you naturally increase your metabolic rate to the maximum peak. Doing so will not only cause pounds of fat to quickly melt off, but it will also ensure that you will not REGAIN pounds back... unlike with fad diets and diet pills!<div>
